name: NBCNews
text:
Cindy McCain endorsed Democratic nominee Joe Biden for president. 

"He will be a commander in chief that the finest fighting force in the history of the world can depend on, because he knows what it is like to send a child off to fight," McCain tweeted. https://t.co/67eUZ6kpo5
